_sText: The map is 100% playable, no holes, glitches, way around things. The only minor thing, is that I put in a Code to an admin room I was never able to finish. If you press the right code, The Door Will Open, but it will be an open space, you can jump outside the map, onto the skybox, and walk about. However if you don't know the code, than this won't happen, considering it's a 7 digit code, I don't think It will happen. :)
